+++ 2024-10-15 · Bradford, UK · SCP-8822

[[div class="croqstyle-responsive-div"]]
||~ [[span class="croqstyle-responsive-div__desktop" style="display: none"]]Experiment[[/span]][[span class="croqstyle-responsive-div__mobile"]]Test[[/span]] || Reality baseline measurement ||
||~ [[span class="croqstyle-responsive-div__desktop" style="display: none"]]Experimenter[[/span]][[span class="croqstyle-responsive-div__mobile"]]Tester[[/span]] || Researcher Vikram Singh ||
